        "paragraph_index": 1,
        "text": "Difference: Δlog K = log β1(en) − log β1(NH3) = 7.32 − 2.72 = 4.60, i.e., ethylenediamine binds ≈ 10^4.6 ≈ 4 × 10^4 times more strongly to Ni2+ than ammonia under comparable aqueous, room‑temperature, low‑ionic‑strength conditions.",
